(14, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Dupad abdominal pads are filled with cellulose fibers making them super-absorbent. The fibers quickly absorb and disperse fluids laterally to prevent pooling and maceration. The backing is constructed of a hydrophobic material which prevents strike-through. All edges are sealed to prevent linting. Latex Free.</p>', 'ABD Pad- Abdominal Pad', '<p>Dupad abdominal pads are filled with cellulose fibers making them super-absorbent. The fibers quickly absorb and disperse fluids laterally to prevent pooling and maceration.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dupad-abdominal-pad', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:19', '2014-12-30 06:29:19', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=dupad-abdominal-pad', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(15, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '', 'Multipad Non-Adherent Wound Dressing-28', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'multipad-non-adherent-wound-dressing-28', '', '', '2014-12-20 22:51:06', '2014-12-20 22:51:06', '', 16, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p_2_8_28.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(16, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>A multi-layered, highly absorbent wound dressing. Gentle non-woven rayon pad between two non-adhering polypropylene contact layers. Will not stick to wound site, damage fragile granulation tissue or traumatize wound upon removal. Absorbs significantly more drainage than similar dressings resulting in fewer dressing changes. Use in place of gauze and tape when more absorbency is needed.</p> <p>Use as a primary or secondary dressing.</p>', 'Multipad Non-Adherent Wound Dressing', '<p>A multi-layered and highly absorbent wound dressing. Will not stick to wound site, damage fragile granulation tissue or traumatize wound upon removal.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'multipad-non-adherent-wound-dressing', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:18', '2014-12-30 06:29:18', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=multipad-non-adherent-wound-dressing', 0, 'product', '', 0),
