(99, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p><span>A highly absorptive, non-adhesive, synthetic sponge composed of polyvinyl alcohol foam, impregnated with Methylene Blue and Gentian Violet, which provide broad-spectrum bacteriostatic protection. It is effective against a variety of microorganisms including MRSA and VRE. It has high filtering efficiency, extreme softness, excellent wicking and retention properties. The 2.5" ring dressing has a moisture retentive film backing, can be used under an ostomy skin barrier and won\'t interfere with adhesion of the barrier.</span></p>', 'Hydrofera Blue Ostomy Ring', '<p>Hydrofera Blue Ostomy Ring provides broad-spectrum bacteriostatic protection and is effective against microorganisms including MRSA and VRE.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hydrofera-blue-ostomy-ring', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:24', '2014-12-30 06:29:24', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=hydrofera-blue-ostomy-ring', 0, 'product', '', 0),
