(155, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>BEST PRICE AND FREE SHIP. Anasept Â Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel is an extremely safe topical hydrogel with exceptionally rapid broad spectrum bactericidal and fungicidal and virucidal properties. Anasept Antimcrobial Skin and Wound Gel rapidly eliminates antibiotic-resistant strains MRSA and VRE and other dangerous micro-organisms.</p> <p>Anasept Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel may be used for the following wound types: pressure ulcers (stage I-IV) , cuts and abrasions, surgical incisions/wounds, diabetic foot ulcers, Â first and second degree burn, venous stasis ulcers, grafted wounds, and donor sites. Anasept Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel may be used for irritated skin or rashes.</p> <p><strong>Anasept Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel may be used on wounds having no drainage to moderate levels of drainage as it has some absorptive capacity</strong>.</p> <p><em><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;">AnaseptÂ </span><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;">Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel is indicated for use by Health Care Professionals in the management of wounds.</span></em></p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">www.anacapatechnologies.com</span></p> <p>Secondary dressing required to cover.</p>', 'Anasept Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel', '<p>BEST PRICE AND FREE SHIP. Anasept Antimicrobial Skin and Wound Gel is an extremely safe topical hydrogel with exceptionally rapid broad spectrum bactericidal, fungicidal and virucidal properties. FDA-approved to eliminate common infection-causing bacteria as well as antibiotic-resistant strains MRSA VRE and other dangerous micro-organisms.Â </p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'anasept-gel', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=anasept-gel', 0, 'product', '', 0),
