(157, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>BEST PRICE and FREE SHIP. Silver-Sept Gel is a clear, LATEX FREE, antimicrobial, amorphous hydrogel wound dressing that helps to maintain a moist wound environment that is conducive to healing. Silver-Sept will absorb a mild amount of wound exudate and will not stain or discolor tissue. Silver-Sept functions as a long-lasting antimicrobial barrier by inhibiting the growth of bacteria including the antibiotic resistant strains: MRSA &amp; VRE &amp; clinically important fungi such as: Candida albicans and Aspergillus niger.</p> <p>www.anacapatechnologies.com</p> <p>Requires secondary dressing to hold in place.</p>', 'Silver-Sept Gel', '<p>A clear, amorphous, antimicrobial hydrogel that inhibits the growth of bacteria including antibiotic resistant strains such as MRSA VRE and fungi such as Candida albicans and Aspergillus niger.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'silver-sept', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=silver-sept', 0, 'product', '', 0),
