(161, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Provides moisture to the wound bed, a cooling effect for first- and second-degree burns, and promotes autolytic debridement.Â Latex-free.</p> <p><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;">A secondary dressing is required to hold in place</span></p>', 'ReliaMed Hydrogel Sheet', '<p>Provides moisture to the wound bed and a cooling effect for first- and second-degree burns.Â </p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reliamed-hydrogel-sheet', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:23', '2014-12-30 06:29:23', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=reliamed-hydrogel-sheet', 0, 'product', '', 0),
