(167, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Hypergel is a water-based hypertonic saline gel that effectively softens and debrides dry necrosis (eschar) to create an optimal environment for natural wound healing.Â </p> <p>Secondary dressing required to hold in place.</p>', 'Hypergel', '<p>A water-based hypertonic saline gel that effectively softens and debrides dry, necrotic tissue.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hypergel', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=hypergel', 0, 'product', '', 0),
