(169, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>A hydrophilic Maltodextrin NF wound dressing clinically proven to promote epithelial proliferation and granulation tissue. Quickly fills wound site and rapidly mixes with exudate to form a protective coating that maintains an ideal moisture balance to protect against dehydration. Available as a gel for dry and minimally draining wounds. For use on all wound types. Can be used on infected or hard-to-heal wounds. Specifically formulated to provide topical nutrients to wound sites and create a natural healing environment. Non-toxic and not systemically absorbed. Controls odor while decreasing purulent exudate. Penetrates all wound irregularities to fill tunneling and undermining. Softens necrotic tissue to facilitate debridement.</p> <p>Requires a secondary dressing to cover.</p>', 'Multidex Maltodextrin Gel', '<p>A hydrophilic Maltodextrin NF wound dressing clinically proven to promote the growth of granulation tissue and epithelial proliferation. Quickly fills wound site rapidly mixing with exudate to form a protective coating that maintains an ideal moisture balance to protect against dehydration.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'multidex-maltodextrin-gel', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '2014-12-30 06:29:22', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=multidex-maltodextrin-gel', 0, 'product', '', 0),
