(175, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Xeroform Impregnated Gauze is a sterile non-adhering primary dressing with 3% Xeroform (Bismuth Tribromophenate) and USP Petrolatum in a blend on a fine mesh gauze. Xeroform Gauze is packaged in convenient peel-open tamper proof packages. Xeroform Gauze is: MEDICATED, mildly deodorizing and it\'s bacteriostatic properties inhibit the growth of bacteria in the wound. NON-ADHERING and a compfortable, soothing hypoallergenic dressing, Xeroform it clings and conforms to the wound without sticking. Occlusive Xeroform Gauze inhibits the loss of body fluids and helps to protect the wound site from contamination. A single layer provides effective coverage. Xeroform has a deodorizing and medicating property that is an ideal dressing for all types of open wounds (cancer resections - burns - donor sites - colostomies - urological - proctological procedures - and all surgical incisions. Can be applied to a non-draining or lightly draining wound. Xeroform Gauze dressings provide a moist environment that is conducive to wound healing.</p>', 'Integrity Xeroform Petrolatum Impregnated Gauze', '<p>Xeroform Impregnated Gauze is a sterile non-adhering primary dressing with 3% Xeroform (Bismuth Tribromophenate) and USP Petrolatum in a blend on a fine mesh gauze. Xeroform Gauze is packaged in convenient peel-open tamper proof packages.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'integrity-xeroform-petrolatum-impregnated-gauze', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:25', '2014-12-30 06:29:25', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=integrity-xeroform-petrolatum-impregnated-gauze', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(176, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '', 'Mesalt Impregnated Gauze-107', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'mesalt-impregnated-gauze-107', '', '', '2014-12-20 22:51:37', '2014-12-20 22:51:37', '', 177, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p_1_0_7_107.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(177, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Mesalt supports the cleansing of moderately to heavily discharging wounds including infected wounds.Â </p> <p>How Mesalt works: The discharge from the wound releases the sodium chloride from the dressing. Mesalt effectively stimulates the cleansing of wounds in the inflammatory phase by absorbing exudate, bacteria and necrotic material from the wound and thereby facilitates the natural wound healing process .Easy application.</p> <p>Areas of use: Mesalt is intended for the management of heavily discharging, discharging infected wounds in the inflammatory phase and deep cavity wounds such as pressure ulcers and surgical wounds.Â </p> <p>Requires secondary dressings to hold in place.</p>', 'Mesalt Impregnated Gauze', '<p>Mesalt supports the cleansing of moderately to heavily discharging wounds including infected wounds.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mesalt-impregnated-gauze', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=mesalt-impregnated-gauze', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(178, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '', 'DeRoyal Oil Emulsion Dressing-108', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'deroyal-oil-emulsion-dressing-108', '', '', '2014-12-20 22:51:37', '2014-12-20 22:51:37', '', 179, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p_1_0_8_108.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(179, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>DeRoyal Oil Emulsion Dressing is a sterile, non-adhering dressing made of knitted cellulose fabric impregnated with an oil emulsion blend. It is used as a primary dressing (goes directly in or on a wound). DeRoyal Oil Emulsion Dressing conforms to the wound site without sticking to fragile healing tissue while helping to maintain a moist wound environment conducive to healing. The knitted cellulose fabric is breathable and allows wound drainage to flow away from the wound site into the absorbent cover dressing thus minimizing maceration or irritation. DeRoyal Oil Emulsion Dressing is ideal for dry to heavily draining wounds.</p> <p>Requires a secondary dressing.</p>', 'DeRoyal Oil Emulsion Dressing', '<p>DeRoyal Oil Emulsion Dressing is a sterile, non-adhering dressing made of knitted cellulose fabric impregnated with an oil emulsion blend.Â </p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'deroyal-oil-emulsion-dressing', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:12', '2014-12-30 06:29:12', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=deroyal-oil-emulsion-dressing', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(180, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '', 'ReliaMed Petrolatum Impregnated Gauze-109', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'reliamed-petrolatum-impregnated-gauze-109', '', '', '2014-12-20 22:51:38', '2014-12-20 22:51:38', '', 181, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p_1_0_9_109.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(181, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>White petrolatum properties minimize trauma to the wound. Ideal for Stages II - IV chronic wounds, tunneling wounds and noninfected wounds. Latex-free.</p> <p>www.reliamedproducts.com</p>', 'ReliaMed Petrolatum Impregnated Gauze', '<p>ReliaMed Petrolatum Impregnated Gauze has white petrolatum propertiesthat minimize trauma to the wound.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reliamed-petrolatum-impregnated-gauze', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=reliamed-petrolatum-impregnated-gauze', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(182, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '', 'ReliaMed Xeroform Impregnated Gauze-110', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'reliamed-xeroform-impregnated-gauze-110', '', '', '2014-12-20 22:51:38', '2014-12-20 22:51:38', '', 183, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p_1_1_0_110.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(183, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>ReliaMed Xeroform is a non-adherent dressing for wounds which provides a moist environment conducive to wound healing. The conformable gauze is soft but fine. Reliamed Xeroform is impregnated with 3% bismuth tribromophenate.Â <span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;">Â Removal of these non-adherent dressings causes minimal trauma to both the wound bed and patient. They are the impregnated dressings of choice for applications when mild medication or deodorizing are required. Examples of use include: post operative applications, first and second degree burns and skin grafts.</span></p>', 'ReliaMed Xeroform Impregnated Gauze', '<p>ReliaMed Xeroform is a non-adherent dressing for wounds which provides a moist environment conducive to wound healing. Contains 3% bismuth for mild medication and deodorizing.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reliamed-xeroform-impregnated-gauze', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=reliamed-xeroform-impregnated-gauze', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(184, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '', 'SHUR-CONFORM Oil Emulsion Impregnated Gauze-111', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'shur-conform-oil-emulsion-impregnated-gauze-111', '', '', '2014-12-20 22:51:38', '2014-12-20 22:51:38', '', 185, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p_1_1_1_111.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(185, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Oil Emulsion impregnated dressings are designed to provide non-adherent dressing for wounds and also provide a moist environment conducive to wound healing. They are made of a knitted cellulose acetate fabric coated with a formulated petrolatum emulsion. The knitted fabric allows wound fluid to move through the dressing and into a secondary absorbent dressing. Oil Emulsion dressings are non-adherent. Removal of these dressings causes minimal trauma to the wound bed and patient. Oil Emulsion dressings are commonly used for the management many types of wounds: skin grafts - surgical sites -abrasions lacerations - dermal ulcers - cosmetic surgery sites. Latex Free.</p> <p>Requires a secondary dressing.</p>', 'SHUR-CONFORM Oil Emulsion Impregnated Gauze', '<p>Oil Emulsion impregnated dressings are designed to provide non-adherent dressing for wounds providing a moist environment conducive to wound healing. They are made of a knitted cellulose acetate fabric coated with a formulated petrolatum emulsion.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shur-conform-oil-emulsion-impregnated-gauze', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '2014-12-30 06:29:13', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=shur-conform-oil-emulsion-impregnated-gauze', 0, 'product', '', 0),
