(251, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>Hibiclens kills MRSA, C. diff (in its vegetative state) and other pathogens that are common causes of infection and diseases. Hibiclens the antimicrobial antiseptic skin cleanser can be an effective defense for preventing the spread of MRSA and other staph infections. Its active ingredient CHG5 kills germs on contact and bonds with the skin to eliminate microorganisms.</p>', 'Hibiclens', '<p>Hibiclens kills MRSA, VRE and Â C. diff (in its vegetative state) and other pathogens that are common causes of infection and diseases.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hibiclens', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:14', '2014-12-30 06:29:14', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=hibiclens', 0, 'product', '', 0),
