(255, 1, '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '2013-04-10 17:42:24', '<p>A major breakthrough in delivery of a proven antimicrobial. Unique combination of silver and alginate and maltodextrin designed to create the optimal moist wound environment important to healing. Provides immediate and sustained antimicrobial activity against a broad spectrum of wound pathogens for up to seven days including methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus aureus (MRSA) Staphylococcus aureus and Pseudomonas aeruginosa and E. Coli.</p>', 'Algidex Ag Paste', '<p>Unique combination of silver alginate and maltodextrin designed to create the optimal moist wound environment important to healing.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'algidex-ag-paste', '', '', '2014-12-30 06:29:16', '2014-12-30 06:29:16', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?product=algidex-ag-paste', 0, 'product', '', 0),
