(954, 1, '2014-12-21 00:00:11', '2014-12-21 00:00:11', '<p class="bodytxt">Painful and debilitating chronic wounds caused by diabetes, pressure, venous insufficiency and arterial disease affect millions of Americans. These wounds are frequently treated in nursing offices and physician offices. A patient caring for his own wounds at home between appointments must either purchase supplies or have a wound care provider bill his insurance for wound care dressings.</p>\r\n<p class="bodytxt">Wound Care Resources specializes in providing a complete selection of traditional and advanced wound care dressings for patient use either at home or in the nursing home. Our mission is to seek out and provide the newest, most advanced products on the market so wound care professionals can access whatever will enable each patient to heal faster and with less pain.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '944-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-21 00:00:11', '2014-12-21 00:00:11', '', 944, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?p=954', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(955, 1, '2014-12-22 05:03:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', ' ', '', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-12-22 05:03:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://admedonlinenew.dev:8888/?p=955', 1, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
